{"tid":2152908,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國旗國徽法修正案通過","createTime":"2020-08-12T08:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T09:04:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"45c172ed5c03603eb98c8ce60c382b5e90b939d8","tid":2152908,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/WU37DL4XQMOSTKHCWJDQCVVF2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FWU37DL4XQMOSTKHCWJDQCVVF2I%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5AcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=50738ffe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FWU37DL4XQMOSTKHCWJDQCVVF2I%2F&h=9c589480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/WU37DL4XQMOSTKHCWJDQCVVF2I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國旗國徽法修正案通過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/edOHKeLa9HvGovR3zc22fp-MZnM=/190x118/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3WR5ISVQ4TDPXXV7EYG6FLZFJI.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FedOHKeLa9HvGovR3zc22fp-MZnM%3D%2F190x118%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3WR5ISVQ4TDPXXV7EYG6FLZFJI.gif&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5AcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=07bb2e57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FedOHKeLa9HvGovR3zc22fp-MZnM%3D%2F190x118%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3WR5ISVQ4TDPXXV7EYG6FLZFJI.gif&h=d89d17d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/edOHKeLa9HvGovR3zc22fp-MZnM=/190x118/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3WR5ISVQ4TDPXXV7EYG6FLZFJI.gif</a><br />\n人大常委已通過《國旗法》及《國徽法》修正案。&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人大常委昨除了處理因押後選舉而出現的立法會真空期，也通過《。。。<br />\n。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：篩選傳媒被轟 警：會優化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國旗不得倒掛 隨意丟棄<br />\n<br />\n以往建制派動員大規模上街。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據相關修正草案，國旗及其圖案不得用作商標、產品外觀設計和商業廣告；不得倒掛或以其他有損國旗尊嚴的方式升掛、使用國旗；不得隨意丟棄國旗；大型群眾活動結束後，活動主辦方應當妥善處置活動現場使用的各類國旗。人大常委譚耀宗早前指日後舉辦活動時，參加者將手持國旗隨便棄置，有關做法絕不能容許，而升起國旗後亦不能任由國旗褪色不理。"},{"pid":"cb3b82d916f8eaf5d59e3e960d81fd3e845b20a8","tid":2152908,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />71 果堆"}]}